{{Infobox dungeon |name = Dreamyard |image = [[File:Dreamyard.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Dreamyard. |tokens = 356,500 |location = Between Unova Route 3 & 4 }} '''Dreamyard''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 5,203,000 HP.
